reviewText: Great Christmas themed movies.  Annie Claus is the best!
Title: Holiday Romance Collection: 4 Movie Set

reviewText: I enjoyed all three of the four movies.  The Annie Claus movie I didn't care for at all, but the other 3 were enjoyable to me.  In fact The Most Wonderful Time of the Year is one of my favorite Christmas movies.  For the price I paid for this is was money well spent.  I would highly recommend this DVD.
summary: Great price, good Christmas movie package
